    QUESTION 0 
        ANSWER: http://en.wikipedia.org.wiki/Artemisinin
        FEEDBACK: I agree.  Wikipedia is not peer reviewed.  Those who know nothing at all can add their tuppence worth, and frequently do.
        ANSWER: www.curemalariatoday.com
        FEEDBACK: I agree.  This is a lobbying organisation, not an objective provider of research.
        ANSWER: www.theantimalariafoundation.co.uk
        FEEDBACK: I agree.  This is another lobbying organisation.  Nothing written on this website will be objective.
