        ANSWER: It doesn't inspire confidence.
        FEEDBACK: I agree.  As a non-specialist reader (which some of your readers will be), it feels disappointing that the test board was not tested.  Either give very good reasons for this (running out of time doesn't seem a particularly good reason to miss out something so crucial) or manage your time better so that this crucial stage is incorporated.
