INTRO <font size="4">Leviticus 1. 3-9<br /><br />or<br /><br /><span style="font-style: italic;">The Book of Leviticus</span>, Chapter 1, verses 3-9<br /></font> 
    QUESTION 0 <font size="4">Which of the following biblical quotations is correct?</font> 
        ANSWER: The first style is correct.
        FEEDBACK: That's correct.  Biblical quotations are very economical.
        ANSWER: The second style is correct.
        FEEDBACK: That's incorrect.  The books of the bible are never italicised, and biblical quotations are very economical.
