<p><strong> 2 </strong><a href="http://www.academic.brooklyn.cuny.edu/english/malani/novel"> www.academic.brooklyn.cuny.edu/english/malani/novel </a> </p><!--EndFragment--> 
    QUESTION 0  <font size="4">There are two things missing from this website reference. What are they?</font> 
        ANSWER: The author's name
        FEEDBACK: Correct.  We have no author here.
        ANSWER: The date accessed.
        FEEDBACK: Correct.   The date accessed is crucial.
        ANSWER: There's nothing missing.
        FEEDBACK: Incorrect.  We're missing the author and the date accessed.
