INTRO from a personal statement:<br /><br />I co-ordinated and edited Sixth Year Yearbook, and organised the school-leavers' dance. This involved designing invitations, ordering drink and negotiating with the council for licence.<br /><br /> 
    QUESTION 0 How many of the word  'the' are missing in this text? 
