        FEEDBACK: I agree.  I think the text should read as follows: The focus of my final year project was air quality. I am therefore already up-to-date with the latest information and advice offered by SEPA.  This makes me a strong candidate for this very important job.  As you will see from the attached CV, I also have the necessary IT skills in MS Office and ArcGIS, and also in Air Modelling Software, for example ADMS, AERMOD, NAME and CALPUFF.  (This allows the reader to take in once piece of information before being pushed on to the next.  Always think of the reader.)
