INTRO <font size="4">Job advertisement:<br /><br />Want to gain experience in museums and archives? The Royal Conservatoire has a vacancy for a six month internship in its special collections department starting in Jan 2012. Hours would be 28 hours per week and you'll need a good academic track record, excellent written and verbal communication skills and, if possible, high IT skills (though training will be offered). Do you fit the bill? If so, let us know, in an email, why you'd like the internship and what you'd achieve if it was offered to you. Please attach a full CV with references.<br /><br />Mrs. Anne Hammond<br />Head of Human Resources <br /></font> 
