        FEEDBACK: I disagree.  The point of your CV is maximum impact.  Here, the IT qualification trails in last in a paragraph filled with other information.  This paragraph needs dividing into three paragraphs:  employment; duties; and skills acquired.  That way, no information gets lost. 
