<p>Age UK has a vision of a world in which older people flourish. We aim to improve later life for everyone through our information and advice, campaigns, products, training and research. </p>
<p>The Administrationand Events Coordinator will be a central member of the West Area Hub, supporting the work and impact of local Age UKs across the Area and supporting all aspects of Age UKs work. </p>
