    QUESTION 0 What type of CV would be best to construct for this job?
        ANSWER: Chronological CV.
        FEEDBACK: This would not be wrong, but wouldn't be the best CV to offer.  This advertisement is actually quite vague on hard skill details, but is clearly looking for somebody who is able to turn their hand to all types of support.  I'd say that a CV highlighting your organisational skills, your adaptability and your readiness for any challenge would be appealing.
        ANSWER: Required skills-based CV.
        FEEDBACK: I agree.  Although the advertisement is actually quite vague on hard skill details, the employer is clearly looking for somebody who is able to turn their hand to all types of support, both administrative and practical.  A CV highlighting your organisational skills, your adaptability and your readiness for any challenge would be appealing.
