        FEEDBACK: This is the best option, since this concluding line clearly links the essay to the essay title. 
        ANSWER: While some may argue that developing class consciousness played a role in the uprising, I believe that this was shaped directly by the monarch's actions and thus cannot be used as a case to protect them.
