        FEEDBACK: This line would be fine, except that it's missing a reference.
        ANSWER: Acne is one of the most common complaints to afflict humanity.  Nearly all of us have suffered from it at one time or another, particularly at puberty.
        FEEDBACK: These lines are too general and unsubstantiated for a strong opening.  Try not to generalise, even as a way into a section.
