INTRO <font size="4"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Summative assessment:</span><br /><br />Discuss the relationship between obesity and the development of type 2 diabetes and the long term consequences of type 2 diabetes in adults.<br /><br />Which of the following is the best opening for this assignment?<br /><br /></font> 
