        ANSWER: This study will look at two scales:  the Anthropomorphism Scale Interview;  and the Belief in Paranormal Scale.
        FEEDBACK: An abstract should give an overview of a whole mini-project report.  It is not an introduction.  This is not the best choice.
        ANSWER: The relationship between paranormal beliefs and anthropomorphism in pets is complicated, and given the nature of the relationship, however many experiments are conducted, is likely to remain so.
        FEEDBACK: This reads more like the closing line of an essay than the abstract of a mini-project report.  Not a good choice.
