INTRO <font size="4">Alan Owen lecture and Fiona Meade lab notes<br /><br />K. A. Zittel, Text Book of Paleontology. 1927 Edited by Eastman, 2nd edition.<br /><br />Gould, S. J. Wonderful Life, The Burgess Shale and the Nature of History, 1990.<br /><br />Website http://www.trilobites.infor/trends.htm<br /></font> 
