        Task multiplechoice difficulty 1
INTRO <p>This is the introduction to an MCQ.</p>
    QUESTION 0 <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><strong>What city <span style="color: #ff6600; text-decoration: underline;">from</span> the list <span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration: underline;">below</span> is the capital of<span style="color: #ff0000; text-decoration: underline; font-size: large;"> Peru</span>?</strong></em></span></p>
        ANSWER: <p>Bogota</p>
        FEEDBACK: <p>No, Bogota is the capital of Colombia, drugs capital of the world. Apparently.</p>
        ANSWER: <p>Lima</p>
        FEEDBACK: <p>Nice one, correct! Located in the centre-west of the country, Lima can be found on the Peruvian coast, overlooking the South Pacific Ocean.</p>
        ANSWER: <p>Buenos Aires</p>
        FEEDBACK: <p>Sorry bro, that's the capital city of Argentina, a country located to the South-East of South America.</p>
